series.title: Money Heist
series.description: Money Heist (Spanish: La casa de papel, [la kasa ðe papel], lit. The House of Paper') is a Spanish heist crime drama television series created by Álex Pina. The series traces two long-prepared heists led by the Professor (Álvaro Morte), one on the Royal Mint of Spain, and one on the Bank of Spain, told from the perspective of one of the robbers, Tokyo (Úrsula Corberó). .
